# Connic Composer SDK

<div align="center">

**Build production-ready AI agents with code.**

Define agents in YAML. Extend them with Python. Deploy anywhere.

[![PyPI version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/connic-composer-sdk.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/connic-composer-sdk/)
[![Python 3.10+](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.10+-blue.svg)](https://www.python.org/downloads/)
[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)

[Documentation](https://connic.co/docs/v1/composer/overview) ‚Ä¢ [Quick Start](https://connic.co/docs/v1/quickstart) ‚Ä¢ [Dashboard](https://connic.co/projects)

</div>

---

## Installation

```bash
pip install connic-composer-sdk
```

## Quick Start

```bash
# Initialize a new project
connic init my-agents
cd my-agents

# Validate your project
connic dev

# Test with hot reload
connic login
connic test

# Deploy
connic deploy
```

